sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as UI Thread (AppMainLoop)
    participant Q as Audio Queue (FreeRTOS)
    participant AT as Audio Task (Worker)
    participant HW as LEDC Hardware (PWM)

    UI->>Q: xQueueSend(ToneRequest)
    Note right of UI: Non-blocking (0ms wait)
    
    loop Work Loop
        Q->>AT: xQueueReceive(req)
        Note left of AT: Blocking wait
        AT->>HW: ledc_set_freq()
        AT->>HW: ledc_set_duty()
        Note over AT: vTaskDelay(duration)
        AT->>HW: ledc_stop()
        Note over AT: vTaskDelay(20ms gap)
    end
